<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-orgadd9353">
</div>
</section>
<section id="slide-org228e793">
<h3 id="org228e793">New RC Front Page</h3>
<ul>
<li>Make it easier to browse and find research</li>
<li>Better communicate hosted journals, portals etc. and their focus</li>
<li>Make it easier for authors to submit to the right journal</li>
<li>Show SARAnnouncements and facilitate registration</li>

</ul>
</section>
<section id="slide-orgcfb3eb3">
<h4 id="orgcfb3eb3">New RC Front Page: Sketch 1</h4>

