<section id="slide-orgb407b3c">
<h3 id="orgb407b3c">Titles and metadata for admin (Casper)</h3>
<ul>
<li>Titles and metadata can be directly edited by a portal admin.</li>

</ul>

</section>
<section id="slide-org7b42bc6">
<h3 id="org7b42bc6">Connect-to-Portal</h3>
<ul>
<li>Private expositions can longer be connected to portals</li>
<li>Share status displayed in admin interface</li>

</ul>
</section>
